++ Islands

++++ Main Island:
The main island is your starting point in the world. It contains a chest with placeholder and a singular oak tree.

++++ Desert Island:
The desert island is located just south of the main island. It is made up of sand blocks and a cactus., mining the sand will reveal a chest hidden underneath.




